{"tha-ap550:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap550:0.2":"Bhaddiyavagga ","tha-ap550:0.3":"8 Lomasakangiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap550:1.1":"“Imamhi bhaddake kappe, ","tha-ap550:1.2":"brahmabandhu mahayaso; ","tha-ap550:1.3":"Kassapo nama gottena, ","tha-ap550:1.4":"uppajji vadatam varo. ","tha-ap550:2.1":"Tadaham candano ceva, ","tha-ap550:2.2":"pabbajitvana sasane; ","tha-ap550:2.3":"Apanakotikam dhammam, ","tha-ap550:2.4":"purayitvana sasane. ","tha-ap550:3.1":"Tato cuta santusitam, ","tha-ap550:3.2":"upapanna ubho mayam; ","tha-ap550:3.3":"Tattha dibbehi naccehi, ","tha-ap550:3.4":"gitehi vaditehi ca. ","tha-ap550:4.1":"Rupadidasahangehi, ","tha-ap550:4.2":"abhibhotvana sesake; ","tha-ap550:4.3":"Yavatayum vasitvana, ","tha-ap550:4.4":"anubhotva mahasukham. ","tha-ap550:5.1":"Tato cavitva tidasam, ","tha-ap550:5.2":"candano upapajjatha; ","tha-ap550:5.3":"Aham kapilavatthusmim, ","tha-ap550:5.4":"ajayim sakiyatrajo. ","tha-ap550:6.1":"Yada udayittherena, ","tha-ap550:6.2":"ajjhittho lokanayako; ","tha-ap550:6.3":"Anukampiya sakyanam, ","tha-ap550:6.4":"upesi kapilavhayam. ","tha-ap550:7.1":"Tadatimanino sakya, ","tha-ap550:7.2":"na buddhassa gunannuno; ","tha-ap550:7.3":"Panamanti na sambuddham, ","tha-ap550:7.4":"jatithaddha anadara. ","tha-ap550:8.1":"Tesam sankappamannaya, ","tha-ap550:8.2":"akase cankami jino; ","tha-ap550:8.3":"Pajjunno viya vassittha, ","tha-ap550:8.4":"pajjalittha yatha sikhi. ","tha-ap550:9.1":"Dassetva rupamatulam, ","tha-ap550:9.2":"puna antaradhayatha; ","tha-ap550:9.3":"Ekopi hutva bahudha, ","tha-ap550:9.4":"ahosi punarekako. ","tha-ap550:10.1":"Andhakaram pakasanca, ","tha-ap550:10.2":"dassayitva anekadha; ","tha-ap550:10.3":"Patiheram karitvana, ","tha-ap550:10.4":"vinayi natake muni. ","tha-ap550:11.1":"Catuddipo mahamegho, ","tha-ap550:11.2":"tavadeva pavassatha; ","tha-ap550:11.3":"Tada hi jatakam buddho, ","tha-ap550:11.4":"vessantaramadesayi. ","tha-ap550:12.1":"Tada te khattiya sabbe, ","tha-ap550:12.2":"nihantva jatijam madam; ","tha-ap550:12.3":"Upesum saranam buddham, ","tha-ap550:12.4":"aha suddhodano tada. ","tha-ap550:13.1":"‘Idam tatiyam tava bhuripanna, ","tha-ap550:13.2":"Padani vandami samantacakkhu; ","tha-ap550:13.3":"Yadabhijato pathavi pakampayi, ","tha-ap550:13.4":"Yada ca tam najjahi jambuchaya’. ","tha-ap550:14.1":"Tada buddhanubhavam tam, ","tha-ap550:14.2":"disva vimhitamanaso; ","tha-ap550:14.3":"Pabbajitvana tattheva, ","tha-ap550:14.4":"nivasim matupujako. ","tha-ap550:15.1":"Candano devaputto mam, ","tha-ap550:15.2":"upagantvanupucchatha; ","tha-ap550:15.3":"Bhaddekarattassa tada, ","tha-ap550:15.4":"sankhepavittharam nayam. ","tha-ap550:16.1":"Coditoham tada tena, ","tha-ap550:16.2":"upecca naranayakam; ","tha-ap550:16.3":"Bhaddekarattam sutvana, ","tha-ap550:16.4":"samviggo vanamamako. ","tha-ap550:17.1":"Tada mataramapucchim, ","tha-ap550:17.2":"‘vane vacchami ekako’; ","tha-ap550:17.3":"‘Sukhumalo’ti me mata, ","tha-ap550:17.4":"varayi tam tada vacam. ","tha-ap550:18.1":"‘Kasam kusam potakilam, ","tha-ap550:18.2":"usiram munjapabbajam; ","tha-ap550:18.3":"Urasa panudissami, ","tha-ap550:18.4":"vivekamanubruhayam’. ","tha-ap550:19.1":"Tada vanam pavitthoham, ","tha-ap550:19.2":"saritva jinasasanam; ","tha-ap550:19.3":"Bhaddekarattaovadam, ","tha-ap550:19.4":"arahattamapapunim. ","tha-ap550:20.1":"‘Atitam nanvagameyya, ","tha-ap550:20.2":"nappatikankhe anagatam; ","tha-ap550:20.3":"Yadatitam pahinam tam, ","tha-ap550:20.4":"appattanca anagatam. ","tha-ap550:21.1":"Paccuppannanca yo dhammam, ","tha-ap550:21.2":"tattha tattha vipassati; ","tha-ap550:21.3":"Asamhiram asankuppam, ","tha-ap550:21.4":"tam vidva manubruhaye. ","tha-ap550:22.1":"Ajjeva kiccamatappam, ","tha-ap550:22.2":"ko janna maranam suve; ","tha-ap550:22.3":"Na hi no sangaram tena, ","tha-ap550:22.4":"mahasenena maccuna. ","tha-ap550:23.1":"Evamviharim atapim, ","tha-ap550:23.2":"ahorattamatanditam; ","tha-ap550:23.3":"Tam ve bhaddekarattoti, ","tha-ap550:23.4":"santo acikkhate muni’. ","tha-ap550:24.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap550:24.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap550:24.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap550:25.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap550:25.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap550:25.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap550:26.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap550:26.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap550:26.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap550:27.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma lomasakangiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap550:28.1":"Lomasakangiyattherassapadanam atthamam. "}